{
  "texts": [
    "Although exact unlearning guarantees the removal of data, it is impractical for models of any significant size due to the high computation cost.",
    "For instance, training Llama-2-70B took ∼ 1.7 million GPU-hours on Nvidia A100 GPUs (Touvron et al., 2023).",
    "There is an increasing interest in machine unlearning in the context of LLMs (Jang et al., 2022; Meng et al., 2023; Liu et al., 2024c).",
    "Recent works highlight the importance of selective LLM unlearning to improve parameter efficiency and model adaptability.",
    "(Zhang et al., 2023a; Liu et al., 2024b; Schick et al., 2023)."
  ]
}